I see you've changed the History and Filters from Popups to dropdowns. This is less helpful, however I recognize you have done so for a reason. At least let me suggest you move the "Manage Filters" option to the TOP of the list instead of the bottom. I have a lot of filters and would prefer to see that link up higher.

